entered text.]]\nBut at least it doesn't have fucking video ads.\n\n{{Title text: And it doesn't pop up a box every time asking you to use your real name. In fact, there's no way to set your name at all. You just have to keep reminding people who you are.}}	And it doesn't pop up a box every time asking you to use your real name. In fact, there's no way to set your name at all. You just have to keep reminding people who you are.	https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/undocumented_feature.png	https://xkcd.com/1305/	18	12	2013		2023-09-27 08:07:21.382708
